		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.achievers.com/blog/?post_type=blog&#038;p=28755</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[<div class="email_"><a href="https://www.achievers.com/blog/hr-chatbots/" title="Click here to read this blog" target="_blank"><img width="960" height="540" src="https://www.achievers.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Chatbots_in_HR_960x540px_v1.png" class="attachment-email-template-image size-email-template-image wp-post-image" alt="" loading="lazy" style="display:block;margin-bottom:15px;width:100%!important;height:auto!important;max-width:100%!important;" srcset="https://www.achievers.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Chatbots_in_HR_960x540px_v1.png 960w, https://www.achievers.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Chatbots_in_HR_960x540px_v1-300x169.png 300w, https://www.achievers.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Chatbots_in_HR_960x540px_v1-768x432.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px" /></a></div>
